{"type":"message","id":"6d019efd","parentId":"9bae29ba","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:15:15.276Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8iyvrsazxnam_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2026-03-21 14:15:15 - Context usage: 73% (145208/200000 tokens)\n2026-03-21 14:15:15 - WARNING: Context usage 73% exceeds threshold 60%\n2026-03-21 14:15:15 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7845,"aggregated":"2026-03-21 14:15:15 - Context usage: 73% (145208/200000 tokens)\n2026-03-21 14:15:15 - WARNING: Context usage 73% exceeds threshold 60%\n2026-03-21 14:15:15 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774073715273}}
{"type":"message","id":"6fff4877","parentId":"6d019efd","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:15:22.481Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Context usage is at 73%, which exceeds the 60% threshold. According to the skill, when context exceeds 85% it should automatically create a new session. At 73%, it's not yet at the automatic threshold but it's getting high.\n\nLet me check the current context manager state and see if there's anything in the proactivity memory about this.","thinkingSignature":"b3d89e0d46a35c7e4b8e08ac9715639a460a1e51e8d2e5d5698f173973f6e5d9"},{"type":"text","text":"Context 使用率 **73%**（145,208/200,000 tokens），超过 60% 阈值但未到 85% 自动切换线。\n\n继续观察，暂不需要创建新会话。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1377,"output":117,"cacheRead":38931,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40425,"cost":{"input":0.00041309999999999996,"output":0.0001404,"cacheRead":0.00116793,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00172143}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774073715276}}
